comments: Jones (MEM) is moving alongside Sexton's (UTA) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Jones (MEM) and Olynyk (UTA) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Olynyk (UTA) and Jones (MEM) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs as Olynyk releases away to receive the pass.
Bane (MEM) legally contests Olynyk's (UTA) shot near the rim.
Clarke (MEM) is already in Sexton's (UTA) path and marginal contact occurs as he releases away from the contact.
Clarke (MEM) is already in Sexton's (UTA) path when he absorbs the contact as he firms up over his right leg.
Clarke (MEM) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two steps after his gather.
Sexton (UTA) cleanly blocks Clarke's (MEM) shot near the rim.  Any ensuing arm contact after the shot is blocked is considered incidental.
Sexton (UTA) steps out of bounds while still in possession of the ball.
Clarke (MEM) is already in Beasley's (UTA) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Beasley (UTA) is moving alongside Bane's (MEM) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Bane (MEM) is bracing for the contact from Beasley (UTA) and marginal contact occurs as he releases away from the contact.
Beasley (UTA) legally contests Bane's (MEM) jump shot attempt.
Aldama (MEM) and Markkanen (UTA) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Clarke (MEM) is moving alongside Clarkson's (UTA) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Jones (MEM) does not inbound the ball within five seconds.
Beasley (UTA) goes to, not through, Brooks' (MEM) space and marginal contact occurs as the two come together during the screen.
Bane (MEM) establishes a slightly wide screening position in Sexton's (UTA) path, and some contact occurs to his slightly extended leg.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Bane (MEM) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to Utah.
Clarke (MEM) cleanly dislodges the ball from Sexton (UTA).

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Replay review of the out of bounds called on Clarke (MEM) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Sexton (UTA) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds, and possession is correctly awarded to Memphis.
Brooks (MEM) and Beasley (UTA) briefly engage and disengage during the inbound.
Aldama (MEM) commits a take foul on Markkanen (UTA).
As Aldama (MEM) attempts to tie up Clarkson (UTA), marginal contact occurs as the ball is dislodged.
Clarke (MEM) brushes Clarkson's (UTA) arm and marginal contact occurs as he attempts to pass.
Brooks (MEM) steps forward into Markkanen's (UTA) space and initiates contact with his lower body that affects the shot near the rim.
Brooks (MEM) brings his arm towards Olynyk's (UTA) side and marginal contact occurs in transition.
Olynyk (UTA) is moving alongside Brooks' (MEM) path and marginal contact occurs in transition.
Olynyk (UTA) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to Memphis.
Sexton (UTA) is moving alongside Bane's (MEM) path and marginal contact occurs as Bane loses his footing on the perimeter.
